{"tid":620980,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"求救 隨機熄機","createTime":"2018-04-08T02:19:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-13T09:25:06.000Z","uid":114275,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ea1fedec98b33a95247cf53d9842c4a504abaf65","tid":620980,"uid":114275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T02:19:45.000Z","msg":"問題： <br />\nRandom 熄機 <br />\n畫面會 freeze 幾秒然後黑 screen 再藍 screen <br />\n但係部機仲行緊風扇仲轉 要強行手動 shutdown<br />\n<br />\n多數打緊機 (但係我開得機都多數打機) <br />\n玩 steam indie game,  pixel game 畫質最低<br />\n<br />\n都試過 idle 緊都熄<br />\n時間不定 有時大半日都無事 有時十分鐘<br />\n<br />\n硬件：<br />\nRyzen 5 1600 +  Cooler Master Hyper 212 Led<br />\nASRock AB3SOM PR04 MATX <br />\nD4-2400-8GB ADATA Premier<br />\n275GB 2.5&rdquo;Crucial MX300 SATA3 SSD <br />\nASUS（24D5MT）SATA 24X DVD&plusmn;RW <br />\nToshiba 1TB SATA3 Desktop HD（DT01ACA 100 / 7200RPM / 32MB）<br />\n4GD5 ZOTAC GeForce GTX 1050Ti Mini ZT-P10510A-10L<br />\nCooler Master MWE Bronze 550 / 550W ATX PowerSupply（80PLUS銅牌）<br />\nGTR 223 ATX Case（Green) <br />\n12cm 風扇 x 3<br />\n<br />\n12/ 2017 黃金全新買<br />\n無超頻 <br />\nPrime 95 燒 CPU pass 唔過 70 度<br />\nFurmark 燒 GPU  pass 唔過 50 度<br />\n<br />\n軟件：<br />\nWin 10 <br />\nEvent log 睇過好似無乜可疑野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n求求各位大佬幫幫手 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c34159aaa7b1d1c0963715eadd396c54c8dc2527","tid":620980,"uid":114275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T02:21:11.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ebfd73a4771fbaa0bc94cae0f5c9959e7bfcb98","tid":620980,"uid":114275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T02:45:08.000Z","msg":"負評可唔可以講下點解<br />\n唔該各位"},{"pid":"0760e14bc967511c06f4ba4c0fb050fbd99d5702","tid":620980,"uid":114275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T03:08:41.000Z","msg":"Help"},{"p